<title>USA: TABLE - Datascope Q4 net up before charges.</title>
<headline>TABLE - Datascope Q4 net up before charges.</headline>
<dateline>MONTVALE, N.J. 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Datascope Corp.</p>
<p>			    Summary of Operating Results</p>
<p>			    Year Ended	   3 Months Ended</p>
<p>		   6/30/97     6/30/96	6/30/97	6/30/96</p>
<p>Net Sales $225,600,000 $211,300,000 $62,500,000   $58,500,000</p>
<p>Net Earnings(Loss)</p>
<p>		14,104,000   20,417,000   6,601,000     (833,000)</p>
